nl.marcus.embermg

Class EmberSchemaGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.marcus.embermg.EmberSchemaGenerator

  • public class EmberSchemaGenerator
extends Object
    Generator for an EmberSchema based on the data model known by a Jackson ObjectMapper.

    The resulting schema contains all classes that were added by calling addClass(Class), addHierarchy(Class) and those classes that were encountered recursively by those methods.

    Author:
    Marcus Klimstra

      • getSubTypes

        protected Collection<NamedType> getSubTypes(Class<?> base)

        Parameters:

      • processClass

        protected void processClass(Class<?> cls)
        Processes the specified class by visiting all properties that are known to Jackson. All additional classes that are encountered by visiting these properties will also be processed recursively. Returns an EmberTypeRef that serves as a reference to the class.
        Parameters:
        cls - the class to process.
